Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.38,0:24:11.17,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(296,132)}火憐DaZe！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,月火Da☆Yo！
