Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:14.14,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,176)}我們是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們是兩兄弟的話就是Fire Misters！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.14,0:24:20.73,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,122)}撫子不成為神  誓不回家！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.14,0:24:20.73,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,554)}真麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是Fire Brothers好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,預告篇Quiz！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiz！
